When asked if Shaun was a good prom date, Monzo told reporters that he went beyond her expectations.

'He just pulled out the dance moves,' Monzo said.

'I thought he was going to have trouble keeping up with me but I was like, 'I can't keep up with this.'

Monzo even got a kiss on the cheek from her favorite celebrity and danced on stage behind him while he played with his band.Monzo originally had another date lined up for the prom but he didn't mind when she ditched him for White as his band's performance was mind-blowing for the entire school.

Like Shaun White, Monzo is also an athlete. She will be attending Loyola University Maryland to play basketball and she'll definitely have a good story to tell her teammates.

